wandering mendicants um but here we can translate this as anybody who's on a spiritual path right this isn't just for monks and nuns this is for anybody who is on a spiritual path uh wanting to be released from all suffering so what too so he says the pursuit of sensual pleasure sensual happiness excuse me in sensual pleasure

