now when he says the middle path you see it's not in between sensual pleasure and self-mortification it's not you can have a bit of sensual pleasure and a bit of self-mortification and you'll find the way out no it's above it's transcendent of it right it has the middle path has nothing to do with either the path of self-indulgence or the path of self-aversion so uh this word middle has to be understood as a path which is transcendent of

