um and he's a way that what the so he says what because is that middle way awakened to by the target which leads to nibbana it is this noble eightfold path with right view right intention right speech right action right livelihood right effort right mindfulness and right concentration this because is the middle way awakened to by the targeter which gives rise to vision so

